<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>BP-R1 BOBTAIL BRAKE PROPORTIONING RELAY VALVE AND LQ-5 BOBTAIL LIMITING VALVE - MAINTENANCE - Every year,
        100,000 miles (160,000 km) or 3,600 operating hours
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc id="hl0401204" svcproctype="pm" graphiccount="0">
        <title>
            <emph type="bold">Every year, 100,000 miles (160,000 km) or 3,600 operating hours</emph>
        </title>
        <para>Perform the
            <hotlnk document="s04012_HL0401205.xml" xrefid="hl0401205">OPERATION</hotlnk>AND
            <hotlnk document="s04012_HL0401201.xml" xrefid="hl0401201">LEAKAGE TESTS</hotlnk>described in
            <hotlnk document="s04012_HL0401203.xml" xrefid="hl0401203">SERVICE CHECKS</hotlnk>.
        </para>
        <para>Perform
            <hotlnk document="s04012_HL0401206.xml" xrefid="hl0401206">INSPECTION TEST BP-R1</hotlnk>
            and/or
            <hotlnk document="s04012_HL04012LQ.xml" xrefid="hl04012lq">INSPECTION TEST LQ-5</hotlnk>. If the BP-R1 or
            LQ-5 fails to function as described or valve leakage is excessive, it should be repaired or replaced.
        </para>
        <para>Performance of the inspection tests require two people: one person stationed in the driver's seat of the
            vehicle, and one person stationed to observe the slack adjusters.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
